<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="70">1.3. Customising the header and footer</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Customise the header and the footer of your design. Display your own logo and design the footer content according to your requirements. The store features, for example, are a great way to highlight the features of your online store, such as free shipping.</p>
</div>
<div id="75" class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Customising the header and footer:</p>
</div>
