<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="90">1.4. Customising the item view</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Customise the design of the item view in the <strong>Item view</strong> tab. Select the item name and item information to be displayed in the online store. Furthermore, select which item variations should be displayed in the item overview.</p>
</div>
<div id="100" class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Customising the item view:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Go to <strong>Plugins » Plugin overview</strong>.<br>
→ The plugin overview will open.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on <strong>Ceres</strong>.<br>
→ The plugin will open.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on <strong>Configuration</strong> in the directory tree.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on the <strong>Item view</strong> tab.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Carry out the settings. Pay attention to the information given in table 3.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Save</strong> the settings.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
<table class="tableblock frame-all grid-all spread">
