<p><strong>Item name</strong></p>
</div></div></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
<p>Select <strong>Name 1</strong>, <strong>Name 2</strong> or <strong>Name 3</strong>. Texts for these fields are saved in the <a href="/en/item/managing-items#50"><strong>Texts</strong></a> tab of the item. If <strong>Name 2</strong> or <strong>Name 3</strong> is selected, but no name was saved in the text field, <strong>Name 1</strong> will be used as the item name.</p>
