<p>Register with <a href="https://github.com/join?source=header-home" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>GitHub</strong></a></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Open the <a href="https://github.com/plentymarkets/plugin-ceres" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Ceres</strong></a> project</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Create your own fork of the project</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Change the source code</p>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>For further information about changing the source code, refer to our <a href="https://developers.plentymarkets.com/dev-doc/template-plugins" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>template guide</strong></a>.</p>
</div>
