<h3 id="1200">2.2. Purchasing a theme on plentyMarketplace</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Theme plugins are an easy way of customising the looks of <strong>Ceres</strong>. Various <a href="https://marketplace.plentymarkets.com/plugins/themes" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>themes</strong></a> for <strong>Ceres</strong> are available on plentyMarketplace. Changes made to the theme plugin have no impact on future updates of the template plugin <strong>Ceres</strong>.</p>
</div>
